4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed for aspiring tech professionals. In this intensive 18-week program, students master essential programming languages like JavaScript and Python. The curriculum includes algorithm scripting, web development, and the use of APIs to create functional applications. 

